features: Refuse to be One-size-fits-all: Unique fluted glass door, slanting drawer surface, and golden knobs embellished this tall white dresser, making the white dresser an eye-catching and aesthetically pleasing family must-have storage dresser.

Great Atmosphere Maker: All it takes is a small table lamp to help us get a small room filled with a sense of warmth and ambiance. The light can create an atmosphere through the fluted glass door, and the design of the flap can be turned up to make the items on display.

Larger & Deeper: The 5.16" deep drawer will fulfill most of your storage needs. The white dresser can be placed in the living room, entryway, and kitchen, for your books, decorations, and greenery, or to store your cosmetics, jewelry, etc.

No Bother Looking for A Match: FINETONES have a series of white and gold dressers, end tables, bookshelf, and buffet cabinet that can be chosen for you to match this white 6 drawer dresser, which helps you create an eye-catching and beautiful room.

Built To Last: Superior material gives you a more durable and solid product experience. This white dresser also comes with an anti-tilt kit so it can be fixed to the wall. Smooth running drawers provide more convenience.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Before I had purchased this dresser, I was a little afraid because there was no reviews. But I wanted the dresser bad enough that I felt the need to be the first one to experience it, first of all my package got lost in the mail and got delivered to the wrong place and customer service was spectacular with that and sent out a new one right away and when I got it I was a little intimidated by all of the pieces. But let me tell you you could not mess up building this dresser, everything goes in one spot and one spot only and the instructions are pretty easy to read and the dresser is actually way higher quality than I thought it was going to be. There's so many supports for the drawers and it just looks good. A lot more room in it than I expected. I would definitely purchase from this company again!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 28, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These took forever to put together, so be ready for that! But the directions were relatively clear, and the end result is beautiful! I changed from a more traditional dresser and these two have a lower profile while providing a lot more storage! I love them! I especially like the little top drawer area. I bought some Puck lights here on Amazon and stuff them to the top of the inside. You can still open the top part and it doesn't knock them off. Makes for a really pretty presentation.

reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Bad quality. High price. Very hard to assemble
reviews.reviewText: The product is bad quality since the drawers are misaligned. The capacity of the drawers is too small. Took forever to assemble and found that the item was defective. Seller wouldn’t refund unless it was shipped back which would cost so much more and involves disassembly and loading a heavy dresser. DONT BUY.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful, excellent instructions, easy to put together.
reviews.reviewText: I just moved and have to buy a ton of furniture. This dresser is absolutely beautiful. I started putting it together and marveled half way through at how easy it was to put together. All the pieces fit. The instructions are clear, and that’s so hard to find now a days. And the final look is absolutely beautiful. 10/10 - I’ve ordered a few things from this seller, so I’m beyond excited to finish putting everything together. Excellent quality and highly recommend.
